{"tid":632425,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯搵咗隻熊嚟舉行開球禮","createTime":"2018-04-17T11:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T15:14:58.000Z","uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b66abf00b559cf53376341dad39d5862f00796","tid":632425,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一場第三級別聯賽喺賽前搵嚟一隻受過訓練嘅熊人表演而惹起爭議，有動物組織批評做法唔人道同埋好危險。<br />\n<br />\n呢場由Mashuk-KMV對Angusht嘅俄羅斯第三級別聯賽，賽前由一隻嚟自馬戲團、叫做「Tim」嘅熊人表演，阿Tim由一名馴獸師帶領出場，喺一字排開嘅兩隊球員同埋觀眾席之間坐低，然後向觀眾做出拍掌嘅動作。再之後，阿Tim要用兩隻後腳支撐企起身，接過比賽用嘅波之後，球證再由阿Tim「手上」拎走個波。<br />\n<br />\n呢段短片被放上網之後引起好大迴響，善待動物組織PETA總監艾利莎艾倫話︰「除咗唔人道同完全脫節，利用熊人去交個波畀球證亦係非常危險。熊係俄羅嘅象徵，我哋希望呢個國家嘅人會展示同情心以及民族自豪感，停止再虐待佢哋，唔好再用熊人嚟做噱頭。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180417/58083443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F58083443&d=%2BX6gucXTjJEYRhwp3Uk4ijANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=5dee956a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F58083443&h=2f9cb2f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180417/58083443</a>"},{"pid":"ec1bdceff87a3456137f07aa0fd65b3ece23f12f","tid":632425,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:16:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_g7KmBjYrw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_g7KmBjYrw8&d=%2BX6gucXTjJEYRhwp3Uk4ijANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=0b416e69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_g7KmBjYrw8</a>"},{"pid":"95235e2414fb55104f5cc96f039ee27b44b35180","tid":632425,"uid":46587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"明明就係人扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80eb88b923203bf5a0c64bc28d5adbecaebeece9","